{"tid":1358554,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"何君堯聲稱朱凱廸包庇支持者打爛其父母墓碑","createTime":"2019-07-24T03:04:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-24T04:54:51.000Z","uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":63,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"9bd6bcbfe841eb187f56e6d87eb231a4b2d9740a","tid":1358554,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T03:04:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1470115_1_L_20190724103753.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1470115_1_L_20190724103753.jpg&h=8bb71265&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n立法會議員何君堯深夜在社交網頁指控，點名是立法會議員朱凱廸的支持者，將他父母的墓碑打爛，而朱凱廸是包庇者，要求他向警方提供資料，交出追隨者。<br />\n<br />\n何君堯在社交網頁的直播中又表示，如果朱凱廸無破壞他父母墓碑，就應率領一眾泛民議員到他父母墓前躹躬，一齊譴責暴力。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1470115-20190724.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1470115-20190724.htm&d=gHNHb7VIn83nczLIzOZu1YLj0gigvT8yTat38OYNh6E%3D&h=e3693993\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1470115-20190724.htm&h=c61ff546\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1470115-20190724.htm</a>"},{"pid":"b8d6bfa7ef1a8d62fb7992e79083b51b99b95170","tid":1358554,"uid":77196,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T03:04:56.000Z","msg":"冇證據老屈<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e105947afb0cce15829f266ca4b3b33cd7b1637","tid":1358554,"uid":144492,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T03:05:13.000Z","msg":"法治？未審先判？<br />\n黑社會真係大哂"},{"pid":"4df4fa7175aaed3b5eff522aeb16786c165ed702","tid":1358554,"uid":264771,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T03:05:18.000Z","msg":"條友痴左線呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class